narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. Fantastic course for anyone interested in journalism, radio, or storytelling. This class gave me a creative outlet to do interesting work.

But for the first couple weeks of the class when we were completing little projects--most of our time was spent working on and in class critiquing of each other's final projects. I probably did ten versions of my final project.
I would recommend Radio Journalism! It was really fun, pretty low-key, and I learned a lot. A good time!
Radio Journalism is a fantastic course for anyone interested in storytelling, writing, or more. Everyone should try to take it, and if you get in--definitely take it!
